{"tid":1027574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國市長「雙飛」心臟病發身亡 中國妓女嚇到落跑","createTime":"2019-02-19T01:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T19:20:34.000Z","uid":216523,"like":196,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"c600c14f065262985e31ca8b16a2422672c0cf37","tid":1027574,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕法國上馬恩省一個市鎮的市長被爆出去年召妓時因心臟病發身亡，兩名中國妓女則嚇到落跑，法國警方正在調查案件細節。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，該名50歲的市長於去年11月11日早上，離開家門要去參加第一次世界大戰終戰百年紀念活動，結果居民們等不到市長出席，一直到下午他也沒有返家，他的妻子趕忙報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，警方後來透過手機定位找到市長，發現他因為心臟病發死在一個公寓中，警方調查得知，市長早上出門參加活動前先找了2名中國妓女買春，卻在辦事前就發病，兩名女子試圖透過針灸、按摩來喚醒他但沒有效果，最後兩人倉皇逃走。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，其中一名妓女已經自首，她在一月中旬的聽證會後，因為沒有協助危難者被拘留，另一人則仍在逃亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2702800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2702800&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b198c6ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2702800&h=3d38a4a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2702800</a>"},{"pid":"8167ad854ea66ddcacd3305979faa969bce4a753","tid":1027574,"uid":155095,"like":482,"dislike":1,"score":481,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"兩名女子試圖透過針灸、<br />\n按摩來喚醒他但沒有效果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010546c40ada5a5438950ccae37e547f7027d585","tid":1027574,"uid":126510,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:48:30.000Z","msg":"中國雞 揚威國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6343b62ee6d9c16ccd588c8ac8b36ef2f6b2ded","tid":1027574,"uid":36383,"like":301,"dislike":2,"score":299,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:50:58.000Z","msg":"<s